snippet.title: Rugbug Redfern
snippet.description:
Hello everyone! I'm an indie game developer using Unity C# to make games. You can play them on itch.io (link below)! Subscribe and join my discord server (link below) to follow my progress!

For contact, please email me or join my discord server. You can also DM me on Reddit (u/RugbugRedfern)
